description:
Description :
        A Son born from the mysterious Bird of Fate In The Shang Empire, Emperor Xin Is Born And Becomes A World Ruler Of The Shang Dynasty, Brings Great Glory To The Dynasty, He Possesses All Martial Arts In The World, However, after Emperor Xin conquered the country of Qi in the west, he became bored and entered the portal and Crossing into the Modern world. Emperor Xin also found a surprising fact, it turns out that in this world, he is the main character of the novel entitled "The Tyrant Martial Emperor".
